
#1, ApiService class under the network package is responsible for calling the api
#2, Under the AppConstants class there is Domain & apiKey
#3, Detail activity load the data from the home activity and there we display the first 2 record from
    the news array which is passed from the home activity
#4, Local database file and DAO files are under the room package
#5, Test case for the Database class are written
#6, NewsDBTest is under the androidTest which is a test case for sorting and accessing the data on
    room db
#7, Bookmark activity is showing the records from the db